                    <msContents>
                        <summary>The ms includes the Prayer of the Blessed Virgin Mary at Golgotha
                            and three pictures: 1) f. 1v A saint with rosary and priest's crutch in
                            red and black; f. 2r A processional cross, white on black; f. 32r: Virgin
                            and Child, red and black. The name Walättä Giyorgis is found on f. 3r;
                            the name Waldä Maryam is found on f. 31v, written over an
                            erasure.</summary>
                        <msItem xml:id="Add_1863-item1">
                            <locus from="1r" to="34v">1r-34v</locus>
                            <title xml:lang="eng" key="work_21419">Prayer of the Blessed Virgin Mary at Golgotha</title>
